  <brief_title>Gastric Tolerability and Pharmacokinetics of DMMET-01</brief_title>
  <official_title>Gastric Tolerability and Pharmacokinetics of DMMET-01. Daily Intake for 30 Days, in Normal Alimentation Conditions, in Healthy Volunteers.</official_title>
