  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the gastric tolerability and the pharmacokinetics
      of a new drug for the treatment of type 2 diabetes, DMMET-01, in healthy volunteers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
